{"sn14.16:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 14.16 ","sn14.16:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn14.16:0.3":"Sagathasutta ","sn14.16:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn14.16:1.2":"“Dhatusova, bhikkhave, satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:1.3":"Hinadhimuttika hinadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:1.4":"Atitampi kho, bhikkhave, addhanam dhatusova satta samsandimsu samimsu. ","sn14.16:1.5":"Hinadhimuttika hinadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandimsu samimsu. ","sn14.16:2.1":"Anagatampi kho, bhikkhave, addhanam dhatusova satta samsandissanti samessanti. ","sn14.16:2.2":"Hinadhimuttika hinadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandissanti samessanti. ","sn14.16:3.1":"Etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannam addhanam dhatusova satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:3.2":"Hinadhimuttika hinadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:4.1":"Seyyathapi, bhikkhave, gutho guthena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:4.2":"muttam muttena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:4.3":"khelo khelena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:4.4":"pubbo pubbena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:4.5":"lohitam lohitena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:4.6":"evameva kho, bhikkhave, dhatusova satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:4.7":"Hinadhimuttika hinadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:4.8":"Atitampi kho addhanam …pe… ","sn14.16:4.9":"anagatampi kho addhanam …pe… ","sn14.16:4.10":"etarahipi kho paccuppannam addhanam dhatusova satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:4.11":"Hinadhimuttika hinadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:5.1":"Dhatusova, bhikkhave, satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:5.2":"Kalyanadhimuttika kalyanadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:5.3":"Atitampi kho, bhikkhave, addhanam dhatusova satta samsandimsu samimsu. ","sn14.16:5.4":"Kalyanadhimuttika kalyanadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandimsu samimsu. ","sn14.16:6.1":"Anagatampi kho, bhikkhave, addhanam …pe… ","sn14.16:6.2":"etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannam addhanam dhatusova satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:6.3":"Kalyanadhimuttika kalyanadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:7.1":"Seyyathapi, bhikkhave, khiram khirena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:7.2":"telam telena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:7.3":"sappi sappina samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:7.4":"madhu madhuna samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:7.5":"phanitam phanitena samsandati sameti; ","sn14.16:7.6":"evameva kho, bhikkhave, dhatusova satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:7.7":"Kalyanadhimuttika kalyanadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:7.8":"Atitampi kho addhanam … ","sn14.16:7.9":"anagatampi kho addhanam … ","sn14.16:7.10":"etarahipi kho paccuppannam addhanam dhatusova satta samsandanti samenti. ","sn14.16:7.11":"Kalyanadhimuttika kalyanadhimuttikehi saddhim samsandanti samenti”ti. ","sn14.16:8.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","sn14.16:8.2":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","sn14.16:9.1":"“Samsagga vanatho jato, ","sn14.16:9.2":"asamsaggena chijjati; ","sn14.16:9.3":"Parittam darumaruyha, ","sn14.16:9.4":"yatha side mahannave. ","sn14.16:10.1":"Evam kusitamagamma, ","sn14.16:10.2":"sadhujivipi sidati; ","sn14.16:10.3":"Tasma tam parivajjeyya, ","sn14.16:10.4":"kusitam hinaviriyam. ","sn14.16:11.1":"Pavivittehi ariyehi, ","sn14.16:11.2":"pahitattehi jhayihi; ","sn14.16:11.3":"Niccam araddhaviriyehi, ","sn14.16:11.4":"panditehi sahavase”ti. ","sn14.16:11.5":"Chattham. "}